            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1298340</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="p3">自從 NVIDIA 發佈 RTX 50 系列之後，<a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">電競電腦</a>又推向另一層次。而每次新系列推出，好多人會選擇不砌機，而選擇一部頂尖<a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">電競手提電腦</a>，隨時隨地享受遊戲樂趣，在創作應用實行上也大大增加效率。ROG 電競電腦系列除了 <a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/rog-republic-of-gamers/filter?SubSeries=ROG-Flow">ROG Flow</a> 平板系列之外，還有以下小編介紹的全新推出 <a href="https://rog.asus.com/hk/">ROG</a> Strix SCAR 16 (2025) 超強<a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">打機電腦</a>。這部電競電腦搭載 Intel® Core™ Ultra 處理器 ，它配備 Intel Core Ultra 9 275HX 處理器，更搭載全新 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 50 系列 GPU 獨立顯示卡，讓玩家在使用 2.5K (2560 x 1600) 畫質流暢打機之餘，也可開啟光線追蹤等最新圖形技術。電腦更在外型、散熱、升級空間以及螢幕效能上全面提升，獨特 AniMe Vision 燈效、鍵盤與機身圍邊的 RGB 燈效效果更型格，外在同內在，這部<a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">打機電腦</a>都為你帶來全新世代的打機體驗。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05271-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298375" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05271-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05271-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05271-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05305-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298377" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05305-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05305-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05305-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p3">搭載最新最強<b> RTX 50 </b>系列<b> GPU <span class="Apple-converted-space"></span></b>圖形晶片<b>175W</b>超高瓦數輸出</h2><p class="p3">在 <a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/deals/rog/">ROG 手提電腦</a>眾多產品中，這部專為打機而設的頂尖產品 <a href="https://rog.asus.com/hk/">ROG</a> Strix SCAR 16 <a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">電競手提電腦</a>搭載 Intel® Core™ Ultra 處理器可選擇高達 Intel Core Ultra 9 275HX 處理器，以及最高搭載 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 5090 Laptop GPU，Strix SCAR 16 和 18 更配備最高 64GB DDR5-5600MHz 記憶體和 4TB PCIe Gen 4 SSD 超高速儲存裝置，可説是現時最強的電競手提電腦。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coreultraprocessorfa.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coreultraprocessorfa-694x308.png" alt="" width="694" height="308" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coreultraprocessorfa-694x308.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coreultraprocessorfa.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05288.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05288-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05288-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05288.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05262.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298349" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05262-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05262-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05262.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p3">對遊戲玩家而言，<a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">打機電腦</a>重點當然落在全新 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 50 系列圖形處理器，而且在 Turbo 模式下 CPU 可達 55W、GPU 高達 175W 超高瓦數；根據用家需要，選擇 Manual Mode 下 CPU 還可再多獲得 20W，整部電腦功耗可突破 250W，為遊戲、創作軟件帶來超強動力。高規格 GPU 能提供流暢且細緻的畫面，加上 NVIDIA DLSS 4（Multi Frame Generation）技術，在 3A 大作或高幀速電競遊戲中都毫不吃力。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05337.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298392" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05337-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05337-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05337.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲今次測試的主機內置 GeForce RTX 5080 Laptop 圖形晶片</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05251.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298347" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05251-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05251-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05251.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p3">延續「跑車級」設計風格<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>標誌屏幕面蓋，用料上乘</h2><p class="p3">今年的 <a href="https://rog.asus.com/hk/">ROG</a> Strix SCAR 16 進一步昇華了它的「跑車級」充滿未來感的外型設計。電腦蓋用上更多 LED 燈製造更形格的燈效；主機圍邊的 RGB 燈效都繼續有升級，全部都用料上乘。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05318.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298384" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05318-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05318-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05318.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
